        <div class="comment-text  js-comment-text-and-form">
            <div class="comment-body js-comment-edit-hide">
                
                <span class="comment-copy">how would it sort the entire array in desecding order on the basis of zestimate-&gt;amount</span>
                
                <div class="d-inline-flex ai-center">
– <a href="/users/592298/neeraj" title="9,215 reputation" class="comment-user owner">Neeraj</a>
                </div>
                <span class="comment-date" dir="ltr"><a class="comment-link" href="#comment42934144_27228288">
                    <span class="v-visible-sr">Commented</span>
                    <span title="2014-12-01 12:35:04Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0" class="relativetime-clean">Dec 1, 2014 at 12:35</span>
